title: Hour 3 - Kevin Durant to Stay in Brooklyn
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Kevin Durant to Stay in Brooklyn
description:
Dan Patrick reacts to the breaking news of Kevin Durant choosing to remain with the Brooklyn Nets. NBA Veteran G Jamal Crawford joins the show to talk about KD's decision and what it means for the Eastern Conference.
